WEBVTT

00:00:00.320 --> 00:00:45.451
Support Admin Watch on
kissasia.cam or kisskh.org

00:01:42.025 --> 00:01:43.065
It's getting cold.

00:01:44.225 --> 00:01:45.385
The sooner we finish this,

00:01:46.465 --> 00:01:47.665
the sooner I can go to sleep.

00:02:08.345 --> 00:02:10.665
Greetings, Your Majesty.

00:02:22.745 --> 00:02:23.705
I…

00:02:27.785 --> 00:02:28.905
I want food.

00:02:33.705 --> 00:02:35.385
I haven't eaten in a long time.

00:02:44.425 --> 00:02:45.585
Don't go.

00:02:46.665 --> 00:02:47.585
Don't go.

00:02:50.065 --> 00:02:52.705
Don't go! Give me food.

00:02:52.785 --> 00:02:53.625
Don't go!

00:02:54.785 --> 00:02:55.905
Come back!

00:02:55.985 --> 00:02:58.185
Come back! Give me food!

00:02:58.265 --> 00:03:01.065
Give me food!

00:03:01.145 --> 00:03:02.145
Give me…

00:03:02.665 --> 00:03:04.465
Give me some warm food.

00:03:05.745 --> 00:03:08.705
Something warm. Something edible.

00:03:09.865 --> 00:03:11.945
Come back!

00:03:22.385 --> 00:03:23.385
How long have you starved him?

00:03:24.265 --> 00:03:25.105
He's a brat.

00:03:25.185 --> 00:03:27.265
I cooked and sent him food
in the beginning,

00:03:27.345 --> 00:03:29.345
but he asked for the golden milk pastry

00:03:29.425 --> 00:03:31.345
so I just ignored him.

00:03:32.185 --> 00:03:33.505
Now that I think about it,

00:03:34.025 --> 00:03:35.265
it's been two or three days.

00:03:36.025 --> 00:03:37.545
He won't starve to death anyway.

00:03:43.225 --> 00:03:44.185
Huai'an.

00:03:45.225 --> 00:03:47.065
You first treated him coldly

00:03:47.145 --> 00:03:49.145
before offering him a feast.

00:03:49.225 --> 00:03:51.745
Your way of treating an old acquaintance
is quite roundabout.

00:03:51.825 --> 00:03:53.905
We are not close.

00:03:54.425 --> 00:03:55.665
When I was 9 years old,

00:03:56.345 --> 00:03:57.665
we joined the Grand Academy together.

00:03:58.265 --> 00:03:59.465
He was the prince.

00:03:59.545 --> 00:04:02.065
But every time,
I was the one who got first place.

00:04:02.145 --> 00:04:03.545
Soon after,

00:04:03.625 --> 00:04:06.345
I found a small snake in my desk drawer.

00:04:06.905 --> 00:04:08.265
What do you think happened?

00:04:09.745 --> 00:04:11.825
He was the one who put the snake there.

00:04:11.905 --> 00:04:13.625
He thought I wouldn't discover the truth

00:04:14.625 --> 00:04:16.145
and even sent me the antidote.

00:04:17.064 --> 00:04:18.184
What a schemer.

00:04:18.865 --> 00:04:21.745
Once I was 10 years old,
I no longer saw him.

00:04:22.785 --> 00:04:24.705
Later, he became the emperor

00:04:25.385 --> 00:04:26.865
and lived under Yan Fengshan's thumb.

00:04:27.825 --> 00:04:30.865
I'm sure he has his own ways of survival.

00:04:32.185 --> 00:04:33.265
It's done.

00:04:36.625 --> 00:04:38.145
A fortunate fellow indeed.

00:04:38.665 --> 00:04:39.505
Where are you going?

00:04:41.105 --> 00:04:42.345
I'm taking food to that scoundrel.

00:04:46.585 --> 00:04:47.745
I made this meal for you.

00:04:48.465 --> 00:04:49.305
For me?

00:04:49.385 --> 00:04:51.465
You've been risking your life for me.

00:04:51.545 --> 00:04:53.865
Shouldn't I make a meal to thank you?

00:04:58.625 --> 00:04:59.825
Come and eat.

00:05:11.785 --> 00:05:13.825
Is this to be my final meal?

00:05:15.225 --> 00:05:16.065
Don't speak ill fortune.

00:05:16.825 --> 00:05:18.065
Even so, it's still worth it.

00:05:40.625 --> 00:05:43.345
Your life is hanging by a thread.

00:06:15.225 --> 00:06:17.745
The new emperor is looking for you.

00:06:18.425 --> 00:06:19.865
As long as you are still missing,

00:06:20.905 --> 00:06:22.465
his throne won't be secure.

00:06:23.945 --> 00:06:25.545
Yan Fengshan of the Huben Army

00:06:26.065 --> 00:06:28.145
means to use you to start a war.

00:06:29.305 --> 00:06:30.705
When that day comes,

00:06:31.345 --> 00:06:33.345
whether he wins or loses,

00:06:34.345 --> 00:06:36.145
you will still die.

00:06:37.945 --> 00:06:39.665
If you leave this place,

00:06:43.425 --> 00:06:45.025
the only fate waiting for you

00:06:47.345 --> 00:06:48.705
is death.

00:06:54.265 --> 00:06:55.425
You…

00:06:56.185 --> 00:06:57.625
you can save my life?

00:06:58.985 --> 00:07:00.225
Only I know of a way.

00:07:08.025 --> 00:07:10.305
What price must I pay?

00:07:12.225 --> 00:07:14.585
You are the bait I'm using
to deal with Yan Fengshan.

00:07:15.705 --> 00:07:17.185
I'm going to kill Yan Fengshan

00:07:18.065 --> 00:07:19.545
and wipe out the entire Huben Army.

00:07:20.145 --> 00:07:23.745
I need you to help me achieve that goal.

00:07:37.505 --> 00:07:38.425
Who are you?

00:07:44.905 --> 00:07:46.545
It's best that you don't recognize me.

00:07:47.665 --> 00:07:51.705
You should also forget the fact
that you are the emperor.

00:07:52.545 --> 00:07:53.785
I already knew

00:07:53.865 --> 00:07:56.025
what kind of person you were
back in the Grand Academy.

00:07:56.905 --> 00:07:59.745
I also know you have
your own way of staying alive.

00:08:02.705 --> 00:08:04.185
But from today onward,

00:08:05.185 --> 00:08:07.665
you will survive by the rules
I set for you.

00:08:08.385 --> 00:08:09.225
Otherwise,

00:08:13.625 --> 00:08:15.065
-you will die.
-You…

00:08:17.065 --> 00:08:18.065
Are you Liu…?

00:08:18.145 --> 00:08:20.065
That man is dead.

00:08:20.665 --> 00:08:24.385
I am your master now. I am Xie Huai'an.

00:08:29.665 --> 00:08:31.585
BEGINNING OF WINTER, WATER BEGINS
TO FREEZE, THE EARTH BEGINS TO HARDEN

00:08:31.665 --> 00:08:33.185
PHEASANTS ENTER THE WATER FOR CLAMS

00:08:58.625 --> 00:08:59.865
When I entered the city,

00:09:01.745 --> 00:09:03.145
I saw my younger sister.

00:09:05.305 --> 00:09:06.385
Has she been doing well?

00:09:11.185 --> 00:09:12.465
She's doing fine.

00:09:13.185 --> 00:09:14.865
Compared to 15 years ago,

00:09:16.225 --> 00:09:17.425
things here

00:09:19.945 --> 00:09:21.025
are much better.

00:09:22.945 --> 00:09:25.105
My master will be here tomorrow.

00:09:26.345 --> 00:09:30.385
Everything will proceed according to plan.

00:09:32.585 --> 00:09:33.465
All right.

00:09:34.265 --> 00:09:35.625
The vendetta of a gentleman

00:09:36.385 --> 00:09:37.745
leaves no man standing.

00:10:03.905 --> 00:10:07.545
When I received my first month's pay
as a registrar in Huainan,

00:10:08.145 --> 00:10:11.065
I hired an artist
to draw these six portraits.

00:10:11.145 --> 00:10:13.625
That was my seventh year on the run.

00:10:15.625 --> 00:10:18.065
I was afraid that I might forget
these people's faces.

00:10:19.465 --> 00:10:21.625
If I want to destroy the Huben Army,

00:10:21.705 --> 00:10:23.705
I must kill these six first.

00:10:25.145 --> 00:10:27.745
Pu Nichuan. In the 19th year of Qiansheng,

00:10:27.825 --> 00:10:30.185
he scouted for Yan Fengshan
and infiltrated Tiemo.

00:10:30.265 --> 00:10:33.105
When he was trapped,
he waited for help that never came.

00:10:33.185 --> 00:10:34.945
Yan Fengshan deemed him an abandoned pawn.

00:10:35.785 --> 00:10:38.945
Since then,
no one knows whether he's dead or alive.

00:10:42.705 --> 00:10:43.785
Father!

00:10:48.585 --> 00:10:50.425
I know very well
whether he's dead or alive.

00:11:03.185 --> 00:11:04.305
Wei Qianting.

00:11:05.425 --> 00:11:08.705
This man is elusive.
His whereabouts remain unknown.

00:11:17.265 --> 00:11:19.265
I met him seven years ago.

00:11:21.905 --> 00:11:23.625
But he should be

00:11:24.785 --> 00:11:27.545
buried in the reed swamps
of Nanwei Trough now.

00:11:30.545 --> 00:11:31.505
Yan Fengshan.

00:11:31.585 --> 00:11:34.505
He overthrew the emperor
and ruled the court for many years.

00:11:35.105 --> 00:11:37.665
People call him Emperor Yan.

00:11:41.305 --> 00:11:42.705
In the use of shadow guards,

00:11:43.225 --> 00:11:45.385
Yan Fengshan

00:11:45.465 --> 00:11:47.625
is way superior to my father.

00:11:53.265 --> 00:11:55.505
That is because he has
a particular man by his side.

00:11:57.465 --> 00:11:58.985
On the night my family was wiped out,

00:11:59.705 --> 00:12:03.185
he was there as well,
but I couldn't see his face clearly.

00:12:03.265 --> 00:12:05.105
LEGACY OF IMPERIAL FAVOR

00:12:05.745 --> 00:12:07.505
After so many years,

00:12:08.745 --> 00:12:10.665
I still haven't found any clues about him.

00:12:13.985 --> 00:12:16.345
Many within the Huben Army
are hiding in the shadows,

00:12:16.905 --> 00:12:20.225
but everyone knows these two people.

00:12:21.265 --> 00:12:24.345
Qingyi, who is in charge of surveillance
and intelligence.

00:12:24.425 --> 00:12:27.425
He possesses the secrets of many
important officials of the imperial court.

00:12:33.545 --> 00:12:34.585
Liu Ziyan.

00:12:36.905 --> 00:12:38.585
The best assassin of the Huben Army.

00:12:40.065 --> 00:12:41.385
He is in charge of killing.

00:12:42.905 --> 00:12:44.185
Whom shall we deal with first?

00:12:44.865 --> 00:12:47.025
My uncle, of course.

00:12:48.385 --> 00:12:50.345
I've wanted to kill him for so long.

00:12:53.985 --> 00:12:55.025
Aren't you the same?

00:12:55.105 --> 00:12:58.705
As long as he is still alive,
I can't live in peace.

00:12:59.745 --> 00:13:00.785
This day

00:13:01.745 --> 00:13:03.385
will come soon.

00:13:06.465 --> 00:13:10.265
YULONG RIDGE

00:13:50.985 --> 00:13:52.865
Are you here to bid me farewell?

00:13:55.465 --> 00:13:56.745
I'm afraid

00:13:59.865 --> 00:14:01.905
this is my last time serving you.

00:14:05.025 --> 00:14:07.505
Xiao Wuyang is not an easy target.

00:14:07.585 --> 00:14:09.465
If the Huben Army
wants to win against him…

00:14:09.545 --> 00:14:10.625
MYSTERIOUS PERSON

00:14:10.705 --> 00:14:12.705
…it won't be a swift victory.

00:14:13.785 --> 00:14:16.185
Why have you been mobilized at this time?

00:14:16.265 --> 00:14:18.385
My subordinate let someone escape.

00:14:18.465 --> 00:14:19.865
We hunted him through the city
for half a month,

00:14:19.945 --> 00:14:20.825
but found nothing.

00:14:21.985 --> 00:14:24.265
That man plays an important role
in the future.

00:14:25.225 --> 00:14:27.665
I must attend to it myself.

00:14:28.465 --> 00:14:30.225
This is interesting.

00:14:39.265 --> 00:14:40.905
It is a serious matter.

00:14:41.745 --> 00:14:42.665
Just go.

00:14:43.545 --> 00:14:44.905
The person

00:14:45.785 --> 00:14:48.305
serving you in the future
might not be as meticulous.

00:14:49.265 --> 00:14:50.705
Please be understanding.

00:14:51.345 --> 00:14:56.145
I've been imprisoned in Yulong Ridge
for more than a dozen years.

00:14:56.745 --> 00:14:59.465
I'm already dead inside.

00:15:00.505 --> 00:15:02.305
I'm not picky about my servants.

00:15:04.505 --> 00:15:05.545
Ziyan.

00:15:07.625 --> 00:15:09.345
One more thing.

00:15:09.945 --> 00:15:11.505
Liu Ziwen is your elder brother.

00:15:13.385 --> 00:15:16.145
Yan Fengshan wanted Liu Ziwen dead.

00:15:17.425 --> 00:15:19.985
Why did you do Yan Fengshan's bidding?

00:15:22.825 --> 00:15:24.585
There are many things

00:15:25.785 --> 00:15:27.905
my brother couldn't tolerate,

00:15:29.905 --> 00:15:31.785
but General Fengshan could.

00:15:34.465 --> 00:15:36.265
At the Battle of Chen Valley,

00:15:37.065 --> 00:15:38.585
I saved a civilian.

00:15:39.185 --> 00:15:41.625
His wife died early, leaving him
to care for parents and children.

00:15:42.225 --> 00:15:43.545
The whole family

00:15:44.305 --> 00:15:47.145
made a living through chopping bamboo
and weaving dustpans.

00:15:47.865 --> 00:15:51.185
When a war broke out,
they could no longer make a living.

00:15:51.785 --> 00:15:53.385
A five-year-old child

00:15:54.585 --> 00:15:56.265
sat on a wooden plate

00:15:56.905 --> 00:15:58.465
and ate the bamboo dustpan.

00:15:59.065 --> 00:16:00.665
The bamboo pricked
his torn mouth and lips.

00:16:02.145 --> 00:16:03.625
He was so pitiful.

00:16:05.745 --> 00:16:08.025
However, it's infuriating as well.

00:16:08.625 --> 00:16:11.065
Did that family betray you?

00:16:12.305 --> 00:16:14.305
I almost lost my life there.

00:16:15.185 --> 00:16:18.265
Under my brother's command,
some acts were forbidden.

00:16:18.865 --> 00:16:22.345
He said we killed people to save others.

00:16:22.945 --> 00:16:24.545
But since that day,

00:16:26.585 --> 00:16:27.985
I only kill others

00:16:29.545 --> 00:16:31.585
so no one can kill me.

00:16:38.825 --> 00:16:39.985
That sounds fair enough.

00:16:50.865 --> 00:16:51.985
Ziyan,

00:16:53.185 --> 00:16:54.225
farewell.

00:17:00.705 --> 00:17:02.345
WENYUAN EATERY, HUA'S MUTTON BROTH

00:17:02.425 --> 00:17:03.945
FENG'S CURED HAM SHOP

00:17:04.025 --> 00:17:05.464
WINE HOUSE

00:17:05.545 --> 00:17:06.545
How much are these vegetables?

00:17:06.625 --> 00:17:08.105
Take a look. They are fresh.

00:17:08.184 --> 00:17:10.105
Pick more and I'll give you a discount.

00:17:10.184 --> 00:17:13.665
-This is a little wilted.
-No, thanks.

00:17:13.745 --> 00:17:14.665
Look at something else.

00:17:26.025 --> 00:17:27.345
APOTHECARY

00:18:34.465 --> 00:18:36.065
You always go to extreme lengths.

00:18:37.105 --> 00:18:38.585
The capital is ruled by the emperor…

00:18:38.665 --> 00:18:39.585
STEADFAST AND UPRIGHT

00:18:39.665 --> 00:18:42.145
…yet you dare kill someone as you please.

00:18:43.185 --> 00:18:45.505
The enemies came and asked for your life.

00:18:46.025 --> 00:18:47.745
They even accused my men of harboring you.

00:18:49.065 --> 00:18:50.705
How much longer do you need

00:18:51.985 --> 00:18:54.425
to move on from the Chen Valley incident?

00:18:54.505 --> 00:18:56.945
It's not that I didn't move on,

00:18:57.025 --> 00:19:00.145
but I've chosen another path
after that night.

00:19:01.825 --> 00:19:03.425
You have a blade in your hand

00:19:04.905 --> 00:19:06.545
but you can't see things clearly.

00:19:08.985 --> 00:19:10.105
After today,

00:19:11.025 --> 00:19:12.185
you are no longer of the Huben Army.

00:19:13.785 --> 00:19:14.945
If you make another mistake,

00:19:16.185 --> 00:19:17.465
I will kill you myself.

00:19:22.745 --> 00:19:24.185
A military command is absolute.

00:19:26.025 --> 00:19:27.905
You'd better kill me today.

00:19:29.305 --> 00:19:30.945
Even if you spare me today,

00:19:32.785 --> 00:19:33.865
I might

00:19:36.025 --> 00:19:37.945
not spare you in the future.

00:19:47.625 --> 00:19:49.185
Our brotherhood

00:19:50.865 --> 00:19:51.985
ends

00:19:53.105 --> 00:19:54.505
now.

00:21:12.425 --> 00:21:14.545
My master bought this place.

00:21:14.625 --> 00:21:15.625
It is now private property.

00:21:16.345 --> 00:21:18.345
You must not go in, sir.

00:21:19.705 --> 00:21:21.465
I wanted to visit a familiar place.

00:21:21.985 --> 00:21:24.225
I didn't know
this place had another owner.

00:21:25.025 --> 00:21:26.025
Forgive me.

00:21:28.025 --> 00:21:30.145
Did you use to live here, sir?

00:21:31.945 --> 00:21:33.105
Yes.

00:21:33.185 --> 00:21:35.025
I was

00:21:35.865 --> 00:21:39.025
a superintendent of this residence.

00:21:45.105 --> 00:21:46.625
This courtyard

00:21:47.465 --> 00:21:48.985
must have been exquisite in the past.

00:21:51.305 --> 00:21:56.465
I wonder who once owned this residence.

00:21:57.465 --> 00:22:00.065
Two brothers lived here.

00:22:00.985 --> 00:22:05.145
The elder brother was the owner.
He was highly respected in Chang'an.

00:22:05.825 --> 00:22:06.825
The younger brother

00:22:07.785 --> 00:22:09.865
was more or less educated
and well-mannered.

00:22:09.945 --> 00:22:11.305
He always followed his elder brother.

00:22:11.905 --> 00:22:13.185
Look at this pear tree.

00:22:14.225 --> 00:22:15.265
When winter gave way to spring,

00:22:16.105 --> 00:22:18.025
it'd be full of pear blossoms.

00:22:18.105 --> 00:22:19.425
When the sun set,

00:22:19.505 --> 00:22:22.505
the courtyard would be bright
and full of guests.

00:22:23.025 --> 00:22:26.625
All the officials would be sitting there,
sipping tea and drinking wine.

00:22:26.705 --> 00:22:27.825
As for me,

00:22:27.905 --> 00:22:31.985
I would play
with my master's two children.

00:22:32.065 --> 00:22:33.185
It was so lively.

00:22:37.305 --> 00:22:40.505
So how has this residence
fallen into such decline?

00:22:50.985 --> 00:22:53.745
Young man, are you still

00:22:54.985 --> 00:22:56.705
in your twenties…

00:23:00.065 --> 00:23:02.265
Anyway, you are still young.

00:23:02.345 --> 00:23:07.105
In your life,
there are many things you cannot control.

00:23:07.745 --> 00:23:08.665
A couple of days ago,

00:23:08.745 --> 00:23:12.065
I suddenly remembered I had left something
in this residence.

00:23:12.865 --> 00:23:15.185
Can you do me a favor?

00:23:18.785 --> 00:23:20.105
Help yourself, then.

00:23:22.705 --> 00:23:23.865
Thank you.

00:23:49.465 --> 00:23:52.505
Uncle! My father is still breathing!

00:23:52.585 --> 00:23:53.785
Find a physician, quickly!

00:23:54.785 --> 00:23:55.865
Father!

00:24:07.465 --> 00:24:10.825
It seems like a blade.

00:24:13.025 --> 00:24:16.145
When I had hardships,
I dealt with them with this blade.

00:24:16.225 --> 00:24:17.625
Now, I'm having another hardship.

00:24:17.705 --> 00:24:19.745
So I'm retrieving it for good luck.

00:24:19.825 --> 00:24:20.785
A hardship?

00:24:21.305 --> 00:24:22.425
Like killing someone?

00:24:24.265 --> 00:24:25.625
Your guess

00:24:26.505 --> 00:24:27.705
is close enough.

00:24:53.585 --> 00:24:54.945
Behave now.

00:24:55.945 --> 00:24:57.865
Otherwise, you will die a cruel death.

00:25:15.905 --> 00:25:17.745
LAMB STEW WITH BREAD

00:25:32.265 --> 00:25:33.625
Enjoy your meal.

00:25:34.345 --> 00:25:35.865
Sir, please step inside.

00:25:42.185 --> 00:25:44.305
Sir, shared tables are not permitted.

00:25:44.825 --> 00:25:46.185
Why don't you sit inside?

00:25:46.265 --> 00:25:47.745
There are many empty seats.

00:25:48.465 --> 00:25:50.105
Hey, you.

00:25:50.185 --> 00:25:52.465
I'm talking to you. Did you not hear me?

00:26:00.545 --> 00:26:03.025
-Sir.
-How did you lose him?

00:26:03.625 --> 00:26:04.705
Before leaving Anfu Gate,

00:26:05.225 --> 00:26:06.505
at the palace steps,

00:26:06.585 --> 00:26:08.225
Someone in a black robe stopped me.

00:26:08.985 --> 00:26:10.265
He killed and wounded 17 of our men

00:26:10.785 --> 00:26:11.985
and took the deposed emperor away.

00:26:12.065 --> 00:26:13.025
Survivors say

00:26:13.625 --> 00:26:15.985
they wounded him in four places,
at least, with a blade.

00:26:16.065 --> 00:26:17.305
The blades were poisoned.

00:26:18.425 --> 00:26:19.945
Our men are posted
at all 12 gates of Chang'an.

00:26:20.825 --> 00:26:21.825
No one has sighted him.

00:26:22.425 --> 00:26:24.385
Chang'an might have a million families,

00:26:24.465 --> 00:26:28.585
but there aren't many places
that can harbor a martial arts expert.

00:26:28.665 --> 00:26:30.305
Besides, he is hurt

00:26:30.905 --> 00:26:32.625
and has an important person with him.

00:26:33.225 --> 00:26:36.425
Only a few physicians
can treat the poison on our army's blades.

00:26:37.265 --> 00:26:38.505
Keep investigating.

00:26:40.065 --> 00:26:41.065
Yes, sir.

00:26:56.145 --> 00:26:58.385
-Master.
-Mr. Long.

00:27:01.345 --> 00:27:05.185
ZHU ZHILONG

00:27:18.865 --> 00:27:21.225
Every time you send a letter,
you tell me how you

00:27:22.145 --> 00:27:24.785
endure hardships and wander in suffering.

00:27:26.225 --> 00:27:29.345
Looking at your physique,
it seems like you're doing well.

00:27:30.905 --> 00:27:33.265
Master, Huai'an has nine lives.

00:27:33.345 --> 00:27:34.185
He is very well.

00:27:34.265 --> 00:27:37.225
On the other hand, I, your disciple,
almost lost my life.

00:27:41.345 --> 00:27:42.825
If you died that easily,

00:27:43.345 --> 00:27:44.705
it means I've misjudged you

00:27:44.785 --> 00:27:46.465
and sent someone useless
to protect Huai'an.

00:27:46.545 --> 00:27:48.945
I'm fine. I'm your disciple after all.

00:27:54.905 --> 00:27:55.985
Is he the one?

00:28:08.345 --> 00:28:09.785
A fine choice for the puppet.

00:28:09.865 --> 00:28:12.145
Identical body size.

00:28:13.265 --> 00:28:14.305
Come in.

00:28:33.385 --> 00:28:34.585
You must wait a little longer.

00:28:47.505 --> 00:28:48.465
He…

00:28:50.305 --> 00:28:51.185
He is quite well.

00:28:52.625 --> 00:28:53.985
What illness does he have?

00:28:54.905 --> 00:28:55.745
He isn't ill.

00:28:55.825 --> 00:28:57.185
He just

00:28:57.265 --> 00:28:59.385
can't open his mouth
and ingest food or water.

00:28:59.465 --> 00:29:03.225
He is kept alive only
by drip-feeding the medicine I concocted.

00:29:04.785 --> 00:29:05.625
Why are you doing this?

00:29:05.705 --> 00:29:07.105
To raise a new skin

00:29:08.585 --> 00:29:10.305
for your appearance.

00:29:27.785 --> 00:29:29.465
The Huben Army is looking for you.

00:29:30.665 --> 00:29:31.905
From now on,

00:29:33.105 --> 00:29:35.465
you can never
show your real face to others.

00:29:36.185 --> 00:29:37.705
Otherwise, your life will be in danger

00:29:37.785 --> 00:29:39.385
wherever you are.

00:29:45.065 --> 00:29:46.385
You need to forget

00:29:47.425 --> 00:29:48.265
about yourself.

00:30:32.185 --> 00:30:33.025
It's his turn now.

00:30:33.105 --> 00:30:35.745
Ye Zheng, give him a Breath-holding Pill.

00:30:40.105 --> 00:30:41.505
No, I…

00:30:42.025 --> 00:30:42.945
Wait.

00:30:43.025 --> 00:30:44.665
-Open your mouth.
-Can you wait?

00:30:44.745 --> 00:30:45.905
Wait.

00:31:14.785 --> 00:31:16.305
This face suits him.

00:31:16.945 --> 00:31:19.865
So long as he stays silent,
no one will grow suspicious of him.

00:31:20.625 --> 00:31:22.905
Changing his face is just the first step.

00:31:23.425 --> 00:31:25.145
His movements and bearing

00:31:26.025 --> 00:31:27.625
must slowly change

00:31:28.225 --> 00:31:29.945
until every move of his

00:31:30.025 --> 00:31:32.705
resembles the other person
to complete the transformation.

00:31:34.745 --> 00:31:37.185
If the Huben Army knows
the deposed emperor is here,

00:31:37.265 --> 00:31:38.585
they will surely come here.

00:31:39.345 --> 00:31:40.385
In the end,

00:31:41.145 --> 00:31:42.905
Yan Fengshan will also appear.

00:31:43.545 --> 00:31:45.145
This is my final opportunity.

00:31:45.865 --> 00:31:47.545
Don't play with fire and burn yourself.

00:31:47.625 --> 00:31:50.305
The Huben Army might just assassinate you

00:31:50.385 --> 00:31:53.065
before you can successfully
lure out Yan Fengshan.

00:32:00.825 --> 00:32:02.265
I've steeled myself for death

00:32:03.905 --> 00:32:06.025
since the day I returned to Chang'an.

00:32:15.025 --> 00:32:15.985
Master.

00:32:16.625 --> 00:32:18.225
DEPOSED EMPEROR

00:32:18.305 --> 00:32:20.025
ZHANG MO

00:32:35.905 --> 00:32:38.105
SINGING-STRING TAVERN

00:33:01.705 --> 00:33:03.505
I've looked at a few residences
around here.

00:33:03.585 --> 00:33:04.785
This is the most suitable one.

00:33:05.705 --> 00:33:07.985
The gate in front can be guarded,
and there's a rear exit.

00:33:08.065 --> 00:33:10.905
More importantly,
there are fine restaurants around here.

00:33:12.145 --> 00:33:15.105
There's a market north of this place,
and the Tangshui Alley is not far.

00:33:16.585 --> 00:33:19.265
There's enough foot traffic here.
Being watched will not be a problem.

00:33:20.265 --> 00:33:21.465
The south of this place

00:33:21.545 --> 00:33:23.865
is next to the residents
of Chengqing Neighborhood.

00:33:24.385 --> 00:33:25.225
It's calm too.

00:33:25.945 --> 00:33:26.945
Wonderful.

00:33:27.465 --> 00:33:29.025
The patron is satisfied.

00:33:29.105 --> 00:33:31.145
What say you, Mo, the pageboy?

00:33:34.345 --> 00:33:35.705
Me?

00:33:36.225 --> 00:33:37.185
I think

00:33:37.985 --> 00:33:39.305
it's not bad.

00:33:45.545 --> 00:33:46.705
Your Majesty,

00:33:47.745 --> 00:33:49.825
you exposed yourself
with your reaction just now.

00:33:50.665 --> 00:33:53.545
Remember, you are now the pageboy, Mo.

00:34:01.425 --> 00:34:04.505
Your every movement and manner

00:34:05.225 --> 00:34:06.625
must match the other person.

00:35:01.505 --> 00:35:03.705
Your Majesty, you do look the part now.

00:35:04.985 --> 00:35:05.985
Like whom?

00:35:07.425 --> 00:35:08.305
Like a servant.

00:35:18.425 --> 00:35:19.625
I misspoke.

00:35:25.825 --> 00:35:26.825
It is all right.

00:35:27.705 --> 00:35:28.825
I am a servant.

00:35:34.185 --> 00:35:35.185
A prisoner.

00:35:37.465 --> 00:35:38.865
Xie and the rest

00:35:39.385 --> 00:35:41.305
are doing this for Your Majesty's
own good.

00:35:50.865 --> 00:35:52.025
No one in this world

00:35:53.705 --> 00:35:55.345
treats another well without reason.

00:35:56.505 --> 00:35:57.465
Xie Huai'an cares too much

00:35:58.145 --> 00:36:00.185
about his own interests in this.

00:36:04.225 --> 00:36:05.465
You mustn't tell him about this.

00:36:07.545 --> 00:36:09.425
Don't worry. I'm leaving tomorrow.

00:36:10.225 --> 00:36:12.465
You're leaving? Where for?

00:36:13.345 --> 00:36:15.465
Xie said you had made good progress.

00:36:15.545 --> 00:36:17.465
Therefore, I may go home now.
My home is in Huzhou.

00:36:20.945 --> 00:36:21.985
Huzhou

00:36:22.745 --> 00:36:23.865
is quite far.

00:36:26.185 --> 00:36:28.265
My wife gave birth
to a son and a daughter.

00:36:28.785 --> 00:36:29.705
We are a family of four.

00:36:33.025 --> 00:36:34.345
You are free now.

00:36:37.785 --> 00:36:39.105
I envy you.

00:36:59.305 --> 00:37:01.065
Young Master, may I come in?

00:37:01.905 --> 00:37:03.025
Come in.

00:37:16.065 --> 00:37:17.745
I've avoided a reunion with you

00:37:18.345 --> 00:37:19.865
because there were people around us.

00:37:20.665 --> 00:37:22.425
He is more observant than others.

00:37:22.505 --> 00:37:26.185
It's not a good thing
if he finds out about our past.

00:37:28.345 --> 00:37:29.585
I appreciate

00:37:30.665 --> 00:37:31.505
your concerns.

00:37:37.465 --> 00:37:40.785
On your 10th birthday,
I prepared a pair of shoes,

00:37:41.385 --> 00:37:43.785
wishing you a smooth road ahead.

00:37:45.785 --> 00:37:46.705
However…

00:37:48.585 --> 00:37:52.185
I was shocked to learn
that you were displaced for years.

00:37:59.745 --> 00:38:01.025
I am fortunate to meet you again.

00:38:01.865 --> 00:38:03.185
I've prepared another pair for you.

00:38:15.265 --> 00:38:16.305
Young Master.

00:38:34.305 --> 00:38:35.425
Zhang Mo,

00:38:38.545 --> 00:38:39.665
thank you.

00:38:50.585 --> 00:38:51.665
Please let me

00:38:52.625 --> 00:38:54.225
put them on for you.

00:38:59.745 --> 00:39:02.465
I… I was your pageboy.

00:39:11.225 --> 00:39:12.225
Please allow me

00:39:13.625 --> 00:39:14.745
to serve you

00:39:16.345 --> 00:39:17.585
one last time.

00:39:55.185 --> 00:39:56.665
This path you've chosen

00:39:58.825 --> 00:39:59.985
will be full of hardships.

00:40:02.985 --> 00:40:04.025
Forgive me

00:40:08.665 --> 00:40:10.105
for not being able to accompany you

00:40:12.225 --> 00:40:13.385
along the way.

00:40:23.265 --> 00:40:24.305
Mo,

00:40:26.425 --> 00:40:27.705
your life

00:40:28.865 --> 00:40:30.625
should be your own.

00:40:33.945 --> 00:40:35.145
Go back to Huzhou.

00:40:36.825 --> 00:40:38.025
Your family

00:40:38.945 --> 00:40:40.185
is waiting for you.

00:40:41.905 --> 00:40:44.025
If I'm lucky enough to return alive,

00:40:44.545 --> 00:40:46.425
remember to prepare a jar
of good wine for me

00:40:50.665 --> 00:40:52.665
when I pass by Huzhou.

00:41:10.305 --> 00:41:11.505
From now on,

00:41:12.265 --> 00:41:14.025
you cannot show your real face to others.

00:41:15.545 --> 00:41:18.625
You need to forget about yourself.

00:41:20.145 --> 00:41:21.585
You are now the pageboy, Mo.

00:41:22.945 --> 00:41:24.145
Your Majesty,

00:41:24.665 --> 00:41:26.865
you do look like it now. Like a servant.

00:41:26.945 --> 00:41:29.665
I also know you have
your own way of surviving.

00:41:30.265 --> 00:41:31.505
But from today onward,

00:41:31.585 --> 00:41:34.345
you must survive
with the rules I set for you.

00:41:35.065 --> 00:41:38.025
Otherwise, you will die.

00:41:38.105 --> 00:41:40.225
Give me something to eat. I'm hungry.

00:41:40.305 --> 00:41:42.025
Something edible.

00:41:42.985 --> 00:41:44.185
I may go home now.

00:41:44.265 --> 00:41:46.585
My wife gave birth to a son
and a daughter.

00:41:46.665 --> 00:41:48.145
We are a family of four.

00:41:52.385 --> 00:41:54.145
You are free now.

00:41:59.025 --> 00:42:01.385
Your Majesty, farewell.

00:42:02.945 --> 00:42:04.585
Please be cautious henceforth,
Your Majesty.

00:42:05.105 --> 00:42:06.265
Xie is a kind man.

00:42:06.345 --> 00:42:08.705
I'm sure he will
find you a good place to stay.

00:42:13.265 --> 00:42:14.105
Safe travels.

00:42:48.225 --> 00:42:49.385
Mo!

00:43:03.905 --> 00:43:06.265
Didn't you want me to be exactly like him?

00:43:08.305 --> 00:43:09.985
Take a guess.

00:43:11.425 --> 00:43:12.745
Who is the one

00:43:14.505 --> 00:43:15.545
lying there now?

00:43:19.785 --> 00:43:20.785
Who is it?

00:43:34.985 --> 00:43:36.305
You deserve death.

00:43:38.785 --> 00:43:40.465
You truly deserve to die.

00:44:00.185 --> 00:44:01.345
Mother.

00:44:01.425 --> 00:44:04.265
Why did you prepare so much food?

00:44:04.345 --> 00:44:07.305
-Because Father is coming back.
-Really?

00:44:07.865 --> 00:44:10.585
Yes.
Father will soon return from Chang'an.

00:44:11.745 --> 00:44:13.665
Father is coming back!

00:44:14.185 --> 00:44:15.825
Father is coming back!